{"data":[{"date":"17:04 27/06","title":"Man City mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/man-city-muon-gay-soc-voi-nguoi-hung-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marco Reus \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Reus kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho Dortmund. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/man-city-muon-gay-soc-voi-nguoi-hung-tuyen-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marco Reus \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Marco Reus \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarco Reus \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Marco Reus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport Bild, Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham muon gay soc voi Marco Reus\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Marco Reus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/2/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-marco-reus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Marco Reus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mahrez-len-75-trieu-bang-172-187268.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City quan t\u00e2m Mahrez</span> ho\u1eb7c Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i v\u00e0o b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nZaha s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Palace trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Leicester h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mahrez. Sport Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City s\u1ebd t\u1eeb b\u1ecf hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Marco Reus c\u1ee7a Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Dortmund c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Man xanh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"648","checkdouble":"189750"},{"date":"16:40 27/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 27/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 27/6.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MEXICO VS TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"647","checkdouble":"189755"},{"date":"16:44 27/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo Darmian s\u1eafp r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMatteo Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU t\u1eeb Torino, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. Vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matteo Darmian mu\u1ed1n chia tay MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n Darmian b\u1ecb t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-thua-nhan-darmian-sap-roi-mu-172-176855.html\" target=\"_blank\">Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</span>, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 r\u1eddi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U can giu chan hau ve Darmian\" title=\"M.U can giu chan hau ve Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/29/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-ngay-16-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSky Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Darmian, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qua \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 MU thu v\u1ec1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Roma, Napoli hay Inter Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi Juventus, b\u1edfi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Darmian \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Paratici c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eafp \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, Darmian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"646","checkdouble":"189757"},{"date":"17:32 27/06","title":"MU v\u00e0 Arsenal chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua \"Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham, Sport 1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-Min \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Tottenham, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Son Heung-Min \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Pochettino, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Spurs.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Son Heung-Min \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Dele Alli, Christian Eriksen l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau trung phong Harry Kane.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Tottenham c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf Premier League trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ghi 47 b\u00e0n sau 139 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-Min c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Son Heung-Min</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m. MU v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham, Sport 1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-Min\" title=\"Son Heung-Min\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Du-am-Thuy-Dien-1-0-Han-Quoc-Son-Heung-min-gay-that-vong--hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Son Heung-Min</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 HLV Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-189764.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-189764.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Pochettino mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-troi-chan-ronaldo-han-quoc-172-182334.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Son</span>,&nbsp;\u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Spurs kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"645","checkdouble":"189762"},{"date":"17:19 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng xem Brazil vs Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-brazil.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb th\u1eafng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 90 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\n- <strong>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Brazil vs Serbia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 1h ng\u00e0y 28/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena (Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Brazil -0.95*0:1*0.90 Serbia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.90*2 3/4*-0.97 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia 1h ng\u00e0y 28/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Brazil s\u1ebd b\u1ecb Costa Rica c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang sau 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Nh\u01b0ng ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Gabriel Jesus, Philippe Coutinho xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. 6 ph\u00fat sau, Neymar \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Brazil th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi khi b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Costa Rica b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, cho t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 68 Brazil chuy\u1ec3n qua 4-2-4 v\u1edbi Coutinho \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea1nh m\u1ecf neo Casemiro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica\" title=\"Neymar Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Vi-dieu-nay,-Brazil-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil m\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, Brazil d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n sang 3-3-4 v\u1edbi Casemiro, Thiago Silva v\u00e0 Miranda \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 Marcelo v\u00e0 Fagner d\u00e2ng cao nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Costa Rica r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c Coutinho \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Brazil. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Douglas Costa xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n thay cho Willian. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi qu\u1ea5y r\u1ed1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Costa Rica kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho ghi ban mo ty so cho Brazil\" title=\"Coutinho ghi ban mo ty so cho Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c Roberto Firmino v\u00e0o thay Paulinho c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Brazil nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n b\u00ean trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Costa Rica \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Brazil c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica gi\u00fap Brazil r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n anh gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u1ee9c \u00e9p m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap Selecao c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\">Brazil th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean: L\u1ec5 tr\u1eeb t\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\u2026</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1eebng ph\u00fat t\u1eebng gi\u00e2y c\u1ee9 d\u1ea7n tr\u00f4i \u1edf St. Petersburg, hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda b\u00f3ng ma k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn cho\u00e1ng t\u1eebng m\u1ea3ng t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m kinh...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 nh\u01b0ng h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i (+2 so v\u1edbi +1). C\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean Serbia \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Brazil. C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 2.5 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u1edf n\u00ean khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. Gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y n\u00f3 l\u00ean 2.75 b\u00e0n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi m\u00e0 Serbia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 cho \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 n\u1ebfu Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t h\u00e3n h\u1eefu v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mladen Krstajic c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 c\u1ee9u m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3 s\u1eed n\u1ebfu Serbia ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (O 2 3/4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u1edf tr\u00ean. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ngay nh\u1eefng l\u00fac b\u1ebf t\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Neymar, Willian hay Coutinho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Selecao t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia thang Thuy Si\" title=\"Serbia thang Thuy Si\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Serbia-thang-Thuy-Si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Serbia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o d\u00f9 l\u00e0 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. Serbia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Adem Ljajic, Dusan Tadic, Alex Kolarov t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Alek Mitrovic, Milinkovic-Savic, Nemanja Matic, Nicola Milenkovic, Branislav Ivanovic \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, Kolarov, Ljajic, Tadic, Milivojevic \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. R\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea7m xa, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao. 15 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn Serbia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\n- <strong>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Serbia t\u1eeb 6 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (O 6)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Serbia s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Brazil (-1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189718.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189718.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc-463-189757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc-463-189757.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"644","checkdouble":"189763"},{"date":"17:49 27/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo Darmian s\u1eafp r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMatteo Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU t\u1eeb Torino, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. Vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matteo Darmian mu\u1ed1n chia tay MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n Darmian b\u1ecb t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-thua-nhan-darmian-sap-roi-mu-172-176855.html\" target=\"_blank\">Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</span>, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 r\u1eddi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U can giu chan hau ve Darmian\" title=\"M.U can giu chan hau ve Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/29/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-ngay-16-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSky Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Darmian, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qua \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 MU thu v\u1ec1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Roma, Napoli hay Inter Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi Juventus, b\u1edfi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Darmian \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Paratici c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eafp \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, Darmian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"643","checkdouble":"189764"},{"date":"17:26 27/06","title":"Lingard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 \"chuy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y \u1edf huy\u1ec7n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/doi-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 6-1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, ng\u00f4i sao Man United \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng theo \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Lingard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nLingard \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u1edbn. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a David Beckham, cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate v\u00e0o anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Lingard \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 pressing c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Sterling, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t m\u1eafn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y \u1edf huy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lingard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y \u1edf huy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/doi-tuyen-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\"Lingard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng\" - Phil Jones</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama c\u1ee7a Lingard, trung v\u1ec7 Phil Jones h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i: \u201cChuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 l\u1ea1? T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n. Trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, Jesse \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Jesse lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u2013 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u1eabn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng 2 ch\u00e2n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Jesse Lingard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh\u201d \u2013 Jones ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Phil Jones v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Anh chia s\u1ebb: \u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110T Anh bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lingard l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra, khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi-421-189747.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi-421-189747.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nC\u0110V x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 con c\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 ng\u1ee7 b\u1edfi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Kaliningrad.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Everton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"642","checkdouble":"189765"},{"date":"17:40 27/06","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u201cdi\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/gary-cahill-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 khi l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap Anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gary Cahill ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00f3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh thua l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Kaliningrad \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: \u0110\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i thua cu\u1ed9c \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i Anh vs B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Cahill ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ea1 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Cahill ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ea1 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/gary-cahill-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cahill ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Cahill kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1eady</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Gary Cahill ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 xa m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e3y ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d, Cahill n\u00f3i. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1eabn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t gian nan, d\u00f9 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u1ebf tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn qu\u00e1 xa v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ngang s\u1ee9c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t hay th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-xac-nhan-kha-nang-giu-chan-harry-kane-o-tran-gap-dt-bi-421-189663.html\">HLV Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/wenger-chi-ra-mat-xich-yeu-kem-nhat-cua-dt-anh-421-189626.html\">Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-len-day-cot-tinh-than-truoc-dai-chien-voi-dt-anh-421-189486.html\">Courtois l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lampard-tin-tuong-dan-em-co-the-len-ngoi-tren-dat-nga-421-189484.html\">Lampard tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e0n em c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018-421-189457.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"641","checkdouble":"189768"},{"date":"17:39 27/06","title":"Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/tam-su-se-de-dang-tien-vao-tu-ket.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham \u2013 Jermaine Jenas d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out, v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a ph\u00e2n chia th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, trong khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Harry Kane \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c d\u00e0nh cho x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jermaine Jenas cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jenas d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" title=\"Henderson c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Panama 6-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/tam-su-se-de-dang-tien-vao-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jenas d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Khi b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c hay Brazil g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Gareth Southgate c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. C\u00f2n \u0111i xa h\u01a1n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, ch\u00fang ta r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Jenas d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi-469-189525.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi-469-189525.html\">Carragher: \u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n b\u00f3p n\u00e1t B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jamie Carragher, \u0110T Anh n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi-421-189747.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi-421-189747.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nC\u0110V x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 con c\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 ng\u1ee7 b\u1edfi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Kaliningrad.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"640","checkdouble":"189769"},{"date":"17:53 27/06","title":"Asensio th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/9/12/asensio-thua-nhan-kha-nang-roi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang m\u1ea3i chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Asensio ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Marco Asensio v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao vai tr\u00f2 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Zidane. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Gareth Bale, Isco hay Lucas Vazquez. \u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Asensio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Asensio ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch k\u00edch n\u1ed5 nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn cho sao tr\u1ebb c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\" title=\"Asensio dang noi len tai Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/17/dong-doi-real-ung-ho-marco-asensio-gianh-qbv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;l\u00e0&nbsp;</span>kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1edf Real Madrid l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup. Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 sau h\u00e3y t\u00ednh&rdquo; &ndash; Marco Asensio cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, Asensio c\u00f2n cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, c\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 - 700 tri\u1ec7u euro. M\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, anh ch\u1ec9 gia nh\u1eadp K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng t\u1eeb Real Mallorca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 3 tri\u1ec7u euro 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb, v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Mohamed Salah theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: center;\">Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea-172-189734.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea-172-189734.html\">Hazard n\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nCesc Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha khuy\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-asensio-180-189042.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-asensio.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-asensio-180-189042.html\">3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Asensio</span><br>\r\nMU, PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marco Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"639","checkdouble":"189770"},{"date":"09:29 27/06","title":"Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u201cchuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d HLV Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thay Conte</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau. Vi\u1ec7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Man United c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Antonio Conte b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn CLB b\u1ecb thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i kinh t\u1ebf. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Conte c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia c\u00f9ng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri - ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00ean thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri - ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00ean thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Chelsea-va-Napoli-dam-phan-vi-HLV-Sarri---nguoi-len-thay-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n sa th\u1ea3i Conte</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch trong \u0111\u00f3 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Laurent Blanc (t\u1ef1 do), Slavisa Jokanovic (Fulham) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri (Napoli). <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e0n, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t r\u1eb1ng Sarri l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam Italia c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng thi\u1ebft tha gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Carlo Ancelotti l\u00e0m thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loeno Igsine xac nhan viec HLV Maurizio Sarri den Chelsea.\" title=\"Loeno Igsine x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00ec HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Sarri v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc khi m\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Conte c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sarri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Ngay t\u1eeb gi\u1edd, c\u00f3 tin chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 Gonzalo Higuain, Dries Mertens v\u00e0 Kalidou Koulibaly, \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-conte-chelsea-chua-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-2-sao-khung-172-188922.html\">V\u00ec Conte Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-khien-conte-khong-the-dan-dat-real-madrid-180-188726.html\">Sergio Ramos khi\u1ebfn Conte kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nham-hlv-argentina-thay-the-conte-172-188459.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm HLV Argentina thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-conte-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-188046.html\">HLV Conte c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-hlv-jokanovic-172-187696.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd thay Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"638","checkdouble":"189709"},{"date":"09:17 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Costa Rica (01h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6): Ti\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-thuy-si-vs-costa-rica-01h00-ngay-286-tiem-ngoi-dau-cua-brazil.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng Brazil.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng 1/8\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Costa Rica (1h - 286) b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Costa Rica (1h - 286) b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thuy-Sy-vs-Costa-Rica.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Vladimir Petkovic \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Costa Rica c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t hai ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia. Nh\u01b0ng FIFA \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng treo gi\u00f2 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thuy Si\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y S\u0129\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Brazil-se-gap-kho-truoc-Thuy-Si-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E c\u1ee7a Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. B\u1edfi Xhaka v\u00e0 Shaqiri l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Xhaka ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Trong khi Shaqiri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00e9p m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0a Nati t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 huy c\u1ee7a Lichtsteiner, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t cho nhau c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Valon Behrami c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb khoan ph\u00e1 h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Costa Rica kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Costa Rica t\u1eebng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn \u1edf Brazil c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u0129 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Los Ticos \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat Serbia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Costa Rica v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. S\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Costa Rica l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m. Ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Costa Rica l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 th\u1ea7n g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Navas c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Los Ticos v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi tuy\u1ebfn, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Costa Rica. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Costa Rica:</strong><br>\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Costa Rica s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 th\u1eafng 2-0 n\u0103m 2006 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Costa Rica ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0 n\u0103m 2010<br>\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 4 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i World Cup khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i thu\u1ed9c khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Honduras \u1edf World Cup 2014<br>\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup. Trong 10 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n- Xherdan Shaqiri tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o 5 trong 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf World Cup (4 b\u00e0n, 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o)<br>\r\n- Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf World Cup, ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00fang 1 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n- Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 4 tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Thuy Sy vs Costa Rica\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thuy-Sy-vs-Costa-Rica-(4-2-3-1-vs-3-4-2-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang tai bang E sau 2 luot tran\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/BXH.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Costa Rica:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-giai-man-an-mung-treu-nguoi-serbia-cua-cap-sao-thuy-si-421-189333.html\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng tr\u00eau ng\u01b0\u01a1i Serbia c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p sao Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-serbia-12-thuy-si-421-189316.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"637","checkdouble":"189711"},{"date":"09:19 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6): Chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng F","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-21h00-ngay-276-chung-ket-bang-f.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng 3-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>\u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>21h ng\u00e0y 27/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Kazan Arena<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>\u0110\u1ee9c 0.81*0:1 3/4*-0.87 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.80*3*-0.88 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 21h ng\u00e0y 27/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico, \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. H\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ed1c v\u00e1c h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 76%, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Marco Reus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Toni Kroos \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chat thep de Duc hoi sinh\" title=\"Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i sinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Chat-thep-de-Duc-hoi-sinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin. 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Die Mannschaft gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi ph\u00e2n chia th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 r\u1ee5t r\u00e8 n\u00e0o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH Bang F\" title=\"BXH Bang F\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/BXH-Bang-F.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn. Tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t hay trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00f3ng l\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n do Joachim Loew d\u1eabn d\u1eaft th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Marco Reus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110\u1ee9c. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a HLV Loew, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Dortmund l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Anh t\u1ecf ra \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Timo Werner hay Thomas Muller, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t m\u1edbi tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Reus cua Duc\" title=\"Marco Reus cua Duc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Marco-Reus-cua-Duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Reus gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Werner v\u00e0 Muller \u0111\u00fang ra l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi song \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Werner t\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110\u1ee9c quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c ai l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tin ch\u1eafc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y Werner, Muller r\u1ed3i Gomez ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Die Mannschaft l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n hay Mexico, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u00ed qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng, song tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. \u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m, s\u1ef1 chu\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c trong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi v\u00e0 3 b\u00e0n thua sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Han-Quoc-vs-Mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Son Heung-min h\u1ee9a gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin, c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u1ea5n v\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00e2ng l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho hai m\u0169i khoan ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 Hwang Hee-Chan v\u00e0 Son Heung-Min xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazana Arena s\u1ebd c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n. C\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 3 tr\u00f2n m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xem ra s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nL\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng 3-1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"636","checkdouble":"189712"},{"date":"10:09 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TPHCM vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 18h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-tphcm-vs-can-tho-18h00-ngay-276-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>TPHCM vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TPHCM vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 18h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TPHCM vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 18h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/tphcm-vs-can-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">TPHCM vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> TPHCM vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 r\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec h\u00e3m l\u1ea1i. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 10 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Toshiya Miura kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng. Trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5y, h\u1ecd h\u00f2a 4, thua 6. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0, TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh r\u1edbt m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1p ch\u00f3t BXH, h\u01a1n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 (\u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i. N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd sau s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c. Vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng Tr\u1ea7n Phi S\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1t nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha v\u1edbi TPHCM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo v\u1eady, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 11, khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t phong \u0111\u1ed9 khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 6 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1eafng tay khi \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng nhau nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng. C\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh s\u1ebd ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 tr\u1eadn, H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 3, thua 6.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nH\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh: S\u01a1n H\u1ea3i; Robert \u0110\u1eb7ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt, V\u0103n Ho\u00e0n, Phi S\u01a1n, Quang Nam, V\u0103n Thu\u1eadn, H\u1eefu Tu\u1ea5n, Minh Trung, Gonzalo, Matias.<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i; Cao C\u01b0\u1eddng, Ng\u1ecdc B\u1ea3o, Anh Tu\u1ea5n, T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ed9c, \u00dat C\u01b0\u1eddng, Trung Anh, C\u00f4ng Th\u00e0nh, Patiyo, Luiz.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"635","checkdouble":"189715"},{"date":"10:22 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 18h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-nam-dinh-vs-da-nang-18h00-ngay-276-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 18h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 18h00 ng\u00e0y 276 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-bong-da-tran-da-nang-vs-nam-dinh-18h00-hom-nay-86-bb-baaabSazes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: 2-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eebng 2 th\u00e1ng, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e1m tin khi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi l\u00fac \u1ea5y, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh y\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 song h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi h\u1ecd t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng kh\u00e1c. Song, v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \"h\u1ee9a su\u00f4ng\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 3, th\u1eafng 2. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho v\u00e9 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u01b0a tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00e0 TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i, b\u1edfi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a SLNA, c\u00f2n TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 2-4 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ec7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch khi 7 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u V-League 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng thu v\u1ec1 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 14 tr\u1eadn, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 4, thua 7.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 3, thua 2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nNam \u0110\u1ecbnh: Thi\u1ec7n Eselle; Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, H\u1eefu Qu\u00fd, V\u0103n Qu\u00fd, M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0110\u1ee9c Nam, H\u1ea1 Long, S\u1ef9 Minh, Henry, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Antonio.<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: V\u0103n H\u01b0ng; Anh Quang, Vi\u1ebft Th\u1eafng, Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1eafng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng, Nh\u1eadt T\u00e2n, Thanh Th\u1ecbnh, Louis, Minh T\u00e2m, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Kouassi</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"634","checkdouble":"189716"}]}